"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-31-Who-will-be-the-fastest-in-pool-on-July-31-at-2024-Olympic-Games--1vGC7bb1obK-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  A total of 18 gold medals are there for grabs on Wednesday at the 2024 Summer Olympic Games. CGTN Sports Scene has recommended the following events for your attention:  The cycling BMX freestyle women's park final will happen at Place de la Concorde in Paris at 13:10 (GMT+2).  Sun Jiaqi and Deng Yawen of China will participate in the shooting trap women's final at National Shooting Center at 15:30 (GMT+2).  The artistic gymnastics men's all-round final will take place at the Bercy Arena at 17:30 (GMT+2).  Then at 20:30, China's Yang Junxuan will compete with the world's top swimmers in the women's 100-meter freestyle final at 20:30 (GMT+2) in the Olympic Aquatics Centre at the Paris La Defense Arena.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"